\mathcal{C}^1
\left|\int_{a} ^{\frac{a+b}{2}}f(x) d x - \int_{\frac{a+b}{2}} ^bf(x)dx\right| \le \frac{(b-a)^2}{4} \cdot \max _{x \in [a,b]} |f'(x)|.
 \left|\int_{a} ^{\frac{a+b}{2}}f(x) d x - \int_{\frac{a+b}{2}} ^bf(x)dx\right| =\left|\int_{a} ^{\frac{a+b}{2}}\big[f(x)-f(x+\frac{b-a}{2})\big] d x \right|. 
